Package: mingiPolygons
Title: Function for Identifying Polygon Objects In A Map In Shiny
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given="Martin", family="Mburu", "mmburu961@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person(given="Ted", family="Muthomi", "muthomited@gmail.com", role=c("aut")))
Description: This package is able to select any polgyon object(country, county or state)
    from any map visualization formed by ggplot or any other package extension deployed in Shiny.
    It is an extension of nearPoints() but specifically for maps.
